The calendar has turned to August, and that means the iPhone 17 series is just one month away. Apple has yet to officially announce an event, but it has been rumored that the devices will be announced <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/08/05/apple-iphone-17-event-set-september-9/">on Tuesday, September 9</a>.<br/>
<br/>
